01:56:50.487 --> 01:56:51.362
Oke

787
01:56:51.620 --> 01:56:52.820
Oke

788
01:56:53.019 --> 01:56:54.219
Ja

789
01:57:03.627 --> 01:57:05.027
We hebben hem!

